name: Milestone
description: To me this render represents how hard I have been working to improve on my blender skills. I was really discouraged as a creator in the 3d world and I thought that I was always producing lesser work than someone who uses cinema 4D. However after creating this masterpiece which is a woman and a skeleton doing a handstand wearing a visor spewing a laser. Behind her is a giant metallic mantis.  Shout out to Techkeyz.xyz and Dreamzlofi.xyz and definetly check out their drops as well!!!
